-- Biesse Returns to `Operating Profitability' in First Half, Shares Advance
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-21T10:30:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/biesse-returns-to-operating-profitability-in-first-half-shares-advance.html

          
          
             Biesse SpA said it returned to
“operating profitability” in the first half while it posted a
“double digit” growth in revenue, according to a statement
distributed by the Italian exchange.  
 Biesse also said that orders rose 61 percent in the first
six months of 2010. The stock rose as much as 9.3% in Milan to
5.375 euros.  
          
          


  


        